text: Jens Glücklich (born 10 July 1966) is a German former cyclist who, prior to the German reunification, competed for East Germany. He competed in the track time trial at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1966 births Category:Living people Category:German male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of Germany Category:Cyclists at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Cottbus
